text: Maarten Jurgens (born 18 August 1944) is a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nijmegen
